WEBVTT

00:00:00.131 --> 00:00:05.853
We operate in an environment where technological acceleration directly causes cultural friction.

00:00:06.694 --> 00:00:09.575
The traditional rulebooks of management are obsolete.

00:00:10.155 --> 00:00:17.578
The focus here is the bottom line and immediate strict practical relevance to the complex social systems encountered daily.

00:00:18.859 --> 00:00:26.302
A performance of understanding means actively applying, analyzing, and creating new knowledge to solve undefined challenges.

00:00:27.293 --> 00:00:29.978
Let us look at a simple A versus B judgment.

00:00:30.919 --> 00:00:31.520
Option A.

00:00:32.462 --> 00:00:36.890
A leader memorizes management theories but struggles to resolve a team dispute.

00:00:38.352 --> 00:00:39.033
Option B.

00:00:39.635 --> 00:00:44.102
A leader actively applies a new communication strategy to resolve the dispute.

00:00:45.024 --> 00:00:52.236
Option B is the correct approach because true learning only occurs through practical application in real-world scenarios.
